    <note>Shen(2) Gui [20625] His great grandson, Yan [20628] (q.v.), was lineage kin to Guan [20636] (Wuxing zhi, 17.10a), who was son of Yanming [20632] and nephew of Yansheng [20633] and cousin to Yuqiu [1460], whose father, Yanxiu [20627], was either brother or cousin to Yanming and Yansheng. Therefore, Yuqiu's great grandfather, Yuan [20629], would be lineage (third) cousin to Yan, making Yan's father, Yanxiu, lineage (third) uncle of Yuan. These Shen(2) lived in Wuxing from antiquity when they first took Shen(2) as a surname.</note>
